@page "/privacy"

<div style="max-width:800px; margin:2rem auto; padding:0 1rem;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <h2>Who I am</h2>
    <p>
        This site is operated by Henry Brooks as a personal portfolio and pool league archive for the University of Birmingham Snooker 
        and Pool club between the years of 2023-2026. You can contact me at: 
        <a href="mailto:henbrooks6@email.com">henbrooks6@email.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>What data I store</h2>
    <p>
        The league archive section of this site stores the first name and 
        last name of league participants at the University of Birmingham Snooker and Pool club alongside their scores from each 
        semester. This data is collected and displayed with the consent of 
        each participant.
    </p>

    <h2>Why I store it</h2>
    <p>
        The data is stored solely for the purpose of maintaining a historical 
        record of the pool league results. The lawful basis for processing 
        this data is consent given by each participant.
    </p>

    <h2>How long I keep it</h2>
    <p>
        Data is kept for as long as the league archive is maintained. 
        You can request removal at any time.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the data I hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, contact me at 
        <a href="mailto:henbrooks6@email.com">henbrooks6@email.com</a> 
        and I will action your request within 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2>Data storage</h2>
    <p>
        Data is stored securely on Microsoft Azure servers located within 
        the European Economic Area.
    </p>
</div>